Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being separated \Nfrom his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy comes to the rescue his brother \NAce who has been captured by the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by sneaking into Impel Down - \Nthe greatest prison in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, he is racing to level 5 with \Na help of Buggy the Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm free! I finally got the treasure \Nmark that I always dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down to level 3 or level 4 - it doesn't \Nmatter either way you're a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Blugori! You can't chop \Nme because I ate Chop-Chop fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strongest Man in the Prison! \NPoison Man Magellan Appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished breaking out of my \Ncell! I don't wanna fall to another hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, at least now I have this which means
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seconds away from finding \NCaptain John's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is \Nfind my way out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go! \NTell me the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is level 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worse than the Crimson Hell of \Nlevel 1! It's called Wild Beast Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You had \Nme running like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This floor has all the wild \Nbeasts of hell everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild beasts of hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Well, until I get \Na chance to run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take full advantage \Nof Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a hippo to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's smaller than a regular hippo. Is \Nthat what you'd call a "wild beast"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd! I heard \Nthat level 2 has...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! What's \Nthis thing?! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He's pretty \Nfast for a hippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop admiring it! \NTurn left here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He crashed into the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He runs pretty fast but can \Nonly run in a straight line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really don't mind \Nthat your body got eaten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see! I'm the Chop-Chop \Nman - Buggy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you manage that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my body parts are chopped \Nto pieces, I can move them as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will learn ya! \NYou little hippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy with Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:08:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way I can \Njust get out of here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I saw something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bat, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monster mantis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's too big \Nfor a mantis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cuts like a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be \Nso impressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get chopped up much \Nmore, it'll be a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an amazing fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so relaxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you think he's stuck?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna just go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these really \Nwild beasts of hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not that big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're not \Nas bad as I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 1 was way more \Nterrifying than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you think about it, wild beasts \Nof hell can only really exist in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a wild beast of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What I heard was true!\NWe're gonna get eaten this time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't wanna come to level 2!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to make my escape without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say something?! \NWhat's this creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the most \Nrare kind of mutant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snake born from a\Nchicken's egg - a Basilisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Prison Guard\NBASILISK"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things come \Nfrom chickens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?\NThat's why they call it a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's allowed to roam \Nfree, it'd eat everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they leave it here as a guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this! Alright, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get \Nyour ass kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not so bad! I'll \Njust make my escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest up to you!\NBye, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jailers on level 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We identified the guy that \NBuggy the Clown is with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That Straw Hat?! \N--He's in Impel Down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture them right away!\NDead or alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? \NWhat happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on on level 2?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as Vice Warden \Ntold you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Warden's office is on level \N4 - the Burning Heat Floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole floor except for his \Noffice is a burning inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warden Magellan has terrible digestive \Nproblems so he stays in a bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for about 10 \Nhours every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he needs 8 hours of sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand then there're mealtimes and breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he usually works for \Nabout 4 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it enough for a warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the need arises, \Nhe is the right man. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you \Nwaiting. He is coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention but Warden ate \NVenom-Venom Fruit so he is a poison man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A poison man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you for your trouble!\N--Thank you for your trouble, Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, it was \Na tough battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:46.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be a guest. I'm \Nthe warden, Magellan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Warden of Impel Down\NMagellan\N(Venom-Venom Fruit Eater - Poison Man)"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright!\NWhy is it so bright in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to stay closed up in a dark room!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I want to keep \Nmy heart closed in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being \Nridiculous! Warden,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Momonga and \NBoa Hancock-dono are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a bit pressed for \Ntime, Warden Magellan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! You see, I've got a \Npretty bad case of the runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison soup that I had for \Nbreakfast seems to disagree with me..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you \Nexpect? It's poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a poison man \Nso I love poisons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a saying - \N"Poison quells poison."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an expression.\NThat's why you have diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a venomous \Ntongue, Hannyabal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and retire so \NI can become warden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, silly me! I meant, hurry up \Nand show them "Fire Fist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible \Nmistake you made!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a heartless \Ncolleague I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Be careful \Nwhen you exhale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your breath is poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! That's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That serves you right, \Nstupid vice warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He spews venom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! What did you just \Nbreathe in my face?! That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a beautiful \Nwoman! I'm in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Warden, that's \NWarden's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll become mine in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Warden's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing \Nanswering my phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Can't take it! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be a warden...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get an antidote \Nfor Vice Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Someone's \Nbroken in to Impel Down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! In this prison's entire \Nhistory, no one has ever broken in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a grave error! And \Nyou're responsible, Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they notice our plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer the video!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see the prisoner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go! \NI'm ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Warden! Don't you \Nrealize how serious this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! \NThey haven't replied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd! We've lost contact \Nwith Warden Magellan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and report to the jailers' room on \Neach floor and to Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why he's \Nhere and what he's up to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the guy running around with Buggy \Non level 2 that we saw just now is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pirate, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't reach the \Njailers' room on level 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's everywhere! \NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep trying \Nuntil they reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jailers' room on level \N2! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, jailers' room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fist became huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you \Nso small now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause it's Third Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm reverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of salvation \Nhas descended to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! He \Ndefeated the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat the Basilisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You \Nguys are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have destroyed \Nthe jailers' room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable! They \Nmust be sent from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you \Nare but thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get us keys, too? \NFor the doors and cuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're right \Nthere on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat Luffy! \NWhy is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's not in a cell - looks \Nlike he's on his way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta take this \Nchance, it's now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven hasn't \Nforgotten me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Is this \Nwhat you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Of course, we want it!\N--Give it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that how you ask \Nsomebody for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! We're \Nbegging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no excuse! \NPlease, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What d'you \Nsay? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm giving you this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a favor of Captain \NBuggy-sama! Accept it gratefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of the cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me who has set you free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!\NWe're indebted to you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy is our savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am! Don't you \Never forget my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, unlock all the cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell down here by chance, but if I start \Nchaos, it'll give me a chance to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright, are you happy now? Now, it's my turn!\N--Let me go! Let me go! You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lead me now! \N--Hey! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any hole \Nlike the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the \Nway to level 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I remember all floors \Nof this maze-like prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Stop, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I?! You said \Nthat you'd lead me to level 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lied, I lied! I wanted the \Ntreasure so I lied to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those prisoners are gonna run \Nrampant on this floor and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lied to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! It's your \Nchance to break out in chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just had a dose of reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to escape if the \Nboss of this floor is still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's safer to be in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, Straw Hat! I'll \Nguide you to level 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said that you don't \Nknow the way, Big Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're having trouble on \Nthis floor, I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, \NStraw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me out \Nwithout noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always pay back my debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's 3! That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Look at that weird hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! Candle Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, can you tell \Nwhich is the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a powerful fool who acts \Nonly on instinct. You can't catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mr. 3! I always get \Nthe job done perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know \Nwhere I was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the island with \Nthe Giants! You are San!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Mr. Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:44.61,On Top - Left,,0000,0000,0000,,"Prisoner Number D-0464\NFormer Baroque Works Agent\NMr. 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku! We just got an \Nemergency report from Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm? What happened? Don't \Ntell me it's about Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Straw Hat Luffy \Nhas infiltrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Straw Hat? \NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Bartholomew \NKuma took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what we heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would a pirate \Nsneak into Impel Down?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what he wants but this \Ntime, it's the end of the road for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the place \Nhe finds himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a prison that has held hundreds \Nof thousands of prisoners in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without allowing even a \Nsingle breakout or escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a truly iron-tight, great \Nprison - Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's their blunder to \Nlet him enter in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is absolutely no way that \Nthe kid will walk out of there alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! There was one guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago, he became the first and \Nonly escapee in the history of Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pirate named \NShiki the Golden Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiki the Golden Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago, one man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,became the first and only escapee \Nin the history of Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.19,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Shiki the Golden Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the present, the Straw Hats encounter \Na giant beetle while sailing the seas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and find themselves caught \Nup in Shiki's ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Special Presentation Related to the Movie!\NA Gold Lion's Ambition on the Move!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
